{"HUG":[{"def":"To cower; to crouch; to curl up.","pos":""},{"def":"To crowd together; to cuddle.","pos":""}],"HUGE":[{"def":"Very large; enormous; immense; excessive; -- used esp.","pos":""}],"HUGGER":[{"def":"One who hugs or embraces.","pos":""}],"HUGGER-MUGGER":[{"def":"Privacy; secrecy.","pos":""}],"HUGUENOT":[{"def":"A French Protestant of the period of the religious wars in France in the 16th century.","pos":""}],"HUGUENOTISM":[{"def":"The religion of the Huguenots in France.","pos":""}]}